framework
Class Cell

java.lang.Object
  framework.Cell

public class Cell
extends java.lang.Object

The class specifies the attributes of each cell in the grid of the game. It provides methods for manipulating each cell in the grid.

Author:
Gautham Nagaraju, Akash Kulkarni, Victor Dong, Prakhar Dubey
